txt.en: Melethon is at the Causeway Forts.\n\nYou should speak to Melethon.

'The enemy bases in Osgiliath are controlled by Captains of Mordor. You should defeat as many of these captains as you are able. Their death will surely cause disorder among their ranks.\n\n'I can only hope that no greater foe rises to command their forces.'
Melethon has ordered you to defeat Captains and War-leaders of the enemy forces to cause disorder among their ranks.
'You have done much for the Gondorian army. Victory will surely be ours!'
Morgul Captains and War-leaders can be found in enemy strongholds in Osgiliath.\n\nYou should defeat Morgul Captains and War-leaders.
